Enum ChangeKind

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ChangeKind>
      • com.b2international.commons.ChangeKind
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Change, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ChangeKind>

    public enum ChangeKind
extends java.lang.Enum<ChangeKind>
implements Change
    The type of the change of the particular object.

    The order of enumeration represents priority;
    values that come first will be preferred over values that come later when displaying a change.
